ed the song.<ref name=\"RS\"/><ref name=\"Billboard\"/>\n\n==Critical reception==\n''[[Rolling Stone]]'' described the song as a \"[[Pop music|pop]] ballad about trying to move on\".<ref name=\"RS\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/watch-sam-smith-how-do-you-sleep-video-860975/|title=Sam Smith Dances His Feelings Away in 'How Do You Sleep?' Video|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|last=Zemler|first=Emily|date=19 July 2019|accessdate=19 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video was released alongside the song on July 19. It was directed by [[Grant Singer]], with choreography by [[Parris Goebel]],<ref name=\"Billboard\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8521220/sam-smith-music-video-for-how-do-you-sleep|title=Sam Smith Showcases His Dancing Talents In Music Video for 'How Do You Sleep?': Watch|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|date=19 July 2019|accessdate=19 July 2019}}</ref> and features Smith dancing with a troupe of shirtless male dancers wearing waist trainers.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/sam-smith-shares-video-for-new-song-how-do-you-sleep-watch/|title=Sam Smith Shares Video for New Song 'How Do You Sleep?': Watch|website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|last=Bloom|first=Madison|date=19 July 2019|accessdate=19 July 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Promotion==\nSmith posted on their social media accounts on July 9 that they had an announcement to make the following day.<ref>{{cite tweet|user=samsmith|number=1148592325398007809|title=\ud83d\udd25\ud83e\udde1 sound on \ud83d\udc9b\ud83d\udd25|date=July 9 2019|accessdate= July 10 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://portalpopline.com.br/sam-smith-prepara-anuncio-especial-para-esta-quarta-feira-10/|title=Sam Smith prepara an\u00fancio especial para esta quarta-feira (10)|website=Portalpopline|language=Portuguese|last=Medeiros|first=Kavad|date=9 July 2019|accessdate= July 19 The pre-order link became active on July, 10 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://samsmith.world/HDYS|title=Sam Smith \u2013 How Do You Sleep?|website=samsmith.world|accessdate=10 July 2019}}</ref> and later the same day, Smith formally announced and shared a clip of the song.<ref>{{cite tweet|user=samsmith|number=1148921364377735169|title=HOW DO YOU SLEEP? July 19th|date=10 July 2019|accessdate=10 July 2019}}</ref> The song is featured on [[Now That's What I Call Music! discography|Now That's What I Call Music! 104]].\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019\u20132020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Argentina ([[Argentina Hot 100]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/sam-smith/chart-history/billboard-argentina-hot-100|title=Sam Smith Chart History (Billboard Argentina Hot 100)|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=19 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 94\n|-\n{{single chart|Australia|10|artist=Sam Smith|song=How Do You Sleep?|rowheader=true|accessdate=5 October 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Austria|40|artist=Sam Smith|song=How Do You Sleep?|rowheader=true|accessdate=1 August 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|11|artist=Sam Smith|song=How Do You Sleep?|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 October 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|6|artist=Sam Smith|song=How Do You Sleep?|rowheader=true|accessdate=30 November 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Canada|16|artist=Sam Smith|rowheader=true|accessdate=30 July 2019}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadaac|27|artist=Sam Smith|rowheader=true|accessdate=25 February 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadachrtop40|9|artist=Sam Smith|rowheader=true|accessdate=25 February 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardcanadahotac|16|artist=Sam Smith|rowheader=true|accessdate=25 February 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Chile ([[Monitor Latino]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://charts.monitorlatino.com/top20/Print/chile/general/20200330|title=Chile General|language=Spanish|publisher=[[M